entries.title: Attack on the Pirates in Dantooine Sector
entries.boss_detected: Tactical Computer: < Vessel with veteran insignias on attack vector, weapon systems armed. >
entries.complete: Fantastic job pilot! We struck a blow to the Pirates that will take them a long time to recover from. Head back to base when ready.
entries.dd_boss_taunt_1: Foolish puppet, you should have run while you had the chance!
entries.dd_boss_taunt_2: To us you're just a nuisance, about to be squashed!
entries.dd_boss_taunt_3: Too bad you ran in to me so early in your career, as I mark it's end!
entries.dd_boss_taunt_4: Maybe I should fly using just one hand, to give you a chance?
entries.dd_boss_taunt_5: Your pilot helmet will look good on my trophy rack, fool!
entries.found_loc: The next area of known Pirate activity has been uploaded to your nav computer, proceed when ready.
entries.level_boss: Superior Command: < The Pirates have sent one of their best pilots to take care of you, be careful! >
entries.level_boss_dead: That one has been a dread ever since he came to this sector, great work pilot!
entries.level_increase: Sensors through out the sectors show increased Pirate activity in response to our attacks.
entries.targets_detected: Tactical Computer: < Vessels fitting hunted ship profile on attack vector, weapon systems armed. >
entries.targets_behind: Tactical Computer: < Be aware, vessels trying to target this ship with their weapon systems. Attack originating direction 180 degrees. >
entries.taunt_1: You're not going to survive this fight!
entries.taunt_2: You should turn back while you can!
entries.taunt_3: Your about to learn the foolishness of messing with the Pirates!
entries.taunt_4: You should never have come here, now you will never leave.
entries.taunt_5: Time to add another puppet on my kill list!
